up\">グループ会社</li>\n        </ul>\n\n        <div class=\"location__map_wrap\">\n          <img src=\"/recruit/img/location/img-basemap.svg\" alt=\"イラスト:日本地図\" class=\"location__map_img\">\n          <ul class=\"location__pin_wrap\">\n            <li class=\"head_office_pin\"></li>\n            <li class=\"group pin07\"></li>\n            <li class=\"office pin08\"></li>\n            <li class=\"office pin09\"></li>\n            <li class=\"office pin10\"></li>\n            <li class=\"factory pin11\"></li>\n            <li class=\"group pin12\"></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- SPレイアウト用 -->\n      <div class=\"c-tab sp\">\n        <div class=\"c-tab__wrap\" role=\"tablist\">\n          <button type=\"button\" id=\"tab__01\" class=\"c-tab__item\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"panel_osaka\" tabindex=\"0\">大阪</button>\n          <button type=\"button\" id=\"tab__02\" class=\"c-tab__item\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"panel_kanto\" tabindex=\"-1\">関東・中部</button>\n          <button type=\"button\" id=\"tab__03\" class=\"c-tab__item\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"panel_kyusyu\" tabindex=\"-1\">九州</button>\n          <button type=\"button\" id=\"tab__04\" class=\"c-tab__item\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"panel_indonesia\" tabindex=\"-1\">海外</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"panel_wrap\">\n          <!-- 大阪 -->\n          <div id=\"panel_osaka\" class=\"c-tab__contents\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"tab__01\">\n            <div class=\"c-tab__contents_inner\">\n              <div class=\"wrap\">\n                <h2 class=\"title\">大阪</h2>\n                <ul class=\"location__link\">\n                  <li class=\"office link01\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"js-modal-open\" data-target=\"head_office\">大阪製鐵株式会社本社</button></li>\n                  <li class=\"factory link04\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"js-modal-open\" da